{
  "text": "We know of no prior work analyzing the implementation results of this local government technology initiative. In addition, it is worth noting that, at the theoretical level, this research contributes to the stream of theories and methods that argue for the relevance of understanding the role of technology, organization and contextual factors in the development of e-government services (see [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
